Link : https://leetcode.com/problems/ugly-number/description/

My approach in python :
  class Solution:
      def isUgly(self, n: int) -> bool:
          if n<=0:
              return False
          while n>=1:
              if n==1:
                  return True
              if n%2==0:
                  n=n//2
              elif n%3==0:
                  n=n//3
              elif n%5==0:
                  n=n//5
              else:
                  return False
          return True
